name: Listened to Alonzo Highsmith: General Manager of Football Operations

content.html:
Orange Bowl BoysAlonzo Highsmith – General Manager of Football OperationsShow NotesYou heard the amazing news…now hear from the man himself! Alonzo Highsmith joined us to discuss his new job as the General Manager of Football Operations at the University of Miami. He told us what the job duties will be. How does Ed Reed fit into all of this? How long has this been brewing? All those answers are in this pod.
